Adfonic,is,an,advertising,marketplace,for,mobile,advertising,Adfonic,s,services,allow,mobile,application,developers,and,publishers,to,generate,revenue,through,advertising,in,their,applications,The,Adfonic,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Adfonic,with,their,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,managing,ads,accessing,user,data,and,information,and,managing,templates